      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "Note"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "RAW QUICKSTART\n\nfile_path -> your NEF/CR2/CR3/RAF/ARW.\nhalf_size ON = fast iteration on 36MP+;\nturn OFF for the final full-res pass.\n\nraw_meta carries EXIF focal + real sensor\nsize into the solve: no more 36mm guess.\nThe report names the lensfun profile used\n(derived-spec matches are best-effort).\n\nThe EXR sidecar (atlas_exports/raw_plates)\nis scene-linear Rec.709 primaries — NOT\nACEScg; convert downstream via OCIO."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
